#: ../../../tools/rv/rv-mon-stall.rst:20
msgid ""
"The stalled task (**stall**) monitor is a sample per-task timed monitor that "
"checks if tasks are scheduled within a defined threshold after they are "
"ready."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../tools/rv/rv-mon-stall.rst:23
msgid ""
"See kernel documentation for further information about this monitor: "
"<https://docs.kernel.org/trace/rv/monitor_stall.html>"
